         <div type="translation">
            <ab>OIM 19335, recto: (1) Hatres son of Parates, 1/4 silver (kite) for (2) the price of oil, specification: Thoth, (3) 1/12 silver (kite), Phaophi, 1/6 silver (kite), has written Es(4)minis (on) Egyptian year 36, Hathyr 7.  OIM 19335, verso: (1) Hathyr 12, 1/6 silver (kite), (2) has written Esminis (on) Egyptian year 36, Hathyr 12.</ab>
